title: Booker T - Live At The El Rey (2013 AXS.TV) [FLAC, Audio Only]
description:
Recorded from concert broadcast on AXS.TV.
Performance: Booker T at the El Rey Theater in Los Angeles, June 25, 2013.
Band: Booker T. Jones (Hammond B3 organ, vocals), Darian Gray (drums), Vernon "Ice" Black (guitar), Melvin Brannon (bass), Wes Smith (sax), Chris Bautista (trumpet), and Lemar Guillary (trombone).
Special guests: Jay James (vocals), Poncho Sanchez (percussion), Joshua Ledet (vocals), Ted Jones (guitar), Kori Withers (vocals), Ledisi (vocals), and Anthony Hamilton (vocals).
Concert includes recent songs from Booker T's latest album "Sound The Alarm", plus classic MGs-era tunes.
Recording edited to remove more than 10 minutes of chit chat between songs.
